<L>__{ext wagon on black friars' bridge night}
<A>__{the wagon has stopped in the middle of blackfriar's bridge. it's pouring with rain. valentina, wearing some sort of covering against the rain, climbs out of the hatch and onto the roof of the wagon. here she finds anton pointing excitedly down into the thames.}
<C>__{anton}
<D>__{incredible! i saw somebody d dancing in the air.. under the b bridge..}
<A>__{valentina looks doubtfully at percy who peers morosely out from under his sou wester and shakes his head.}
<C>__{anton }
<D>__{it's true! there was a sh shadow on the water, when the lightning flashed...}
<A>__{lightning flashes again. we see what anton and valentina see. a shadow, on the water, of someone `dancing', hung by his neck with a rope attached to the underside of the bridge.}
<C>__{anton }
<P>__{(triumphant)}
<D>__{you see! the d dancer!}
<C>__{valentina}
<P>__{(horrified)}
<D>__{there's someone hanging there!}
<C>__{anton}
<P>__{(smugly to percy)}
<D>__{i t told you!}
<C>__{valentina}
<D>__{a rope! get a rope!}
